OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMark Esper: Former Pentagon
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchief sues Pentagon over   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fbook release               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Former Pentagon chief Mark Esper has   
OL,6, sued the Pentagon over redactions to   
OL,7, his forthcoming memoir.                
OL,9,FIn a lawsuit filed Sunday, Mr Esper    
OL,10,Faccuses the defence department of      
OL,11,Fcensoring portions of his manuscript   
OL,12,F"under the guise of classification".   
OL,14,FHe was "disappointed" to have his right
OL,15,Fto free speech violated, he said.      
OL,17,FMr Esper was appointed defence         
OL,18,Fsecretary in 2019 by former president  
OL,19,FDonald Trump, who fired him shortly    
OL,20,Fafter the November 2020 election.      
